'''Chirvat-türkisi''' or '''Croatian song''' ({{lang-bs|Hrvatska pjesma}}) is a love song from a manuscript from {{circa|1588/89}}, written in [[Arebica]] by a certain Mehmed in [[Transylvania]]. It also contains a number of German, Hungarian and Latin songs written in the Arabic script. This manuscript is held in the National Library in [[Vienna]].

