'''Serbian Luxembourger''' are citizens of [[Luxembourg]] who are of [[Serbian people|Serbian]] origin. According to the Serbian Ambassador to [[Belgium]] and Luxembourg, there are approximately 7,000 Serbs living in Luxembourg, approximately 1.2% of its population.<ref>Deliso, Chris. "Serbia's Relations with Belgium and Luxembourg: Interview with Ambassador Vesna Arsic." Balkananalysis.com. Balkan Analysis, 12 June 2015. Web. 19 Dec. 2016.</ref>

